n 签订独家内容协议，但微软&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/16 /23792215/sony-microsoft-call-of-duty-cod-deal-signed&quot;>;与索尼达成了一项协议&lt;/a>;，作为承诺的一部分，索尼在收购动视暴雪后将为该系列的未来发行带来平等。微软在收购动视暴雪时不得不做出妥协，以通过监管机构，其中包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/2/21/23608930/microsoft-nvidia-geforce-now-xbox- games-announcement&quot;>;从...带来游戏&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/24/24278406/call-of- Duty-black-ops-6-nvidia-geforce-now-streaming&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/24/24278406/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-nvidia-geforce-now-streaming" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/24/24278406/call-of-duty-black-ops-6-nvidia-geforce-now-streaming</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry></feed>